  "title": "SHIPPING AGENCY OPERATION OFFICER",
  "description": "<p>Job TitleShipping Agency</p>\n<p>OccupationOperations Officer</p>\n<p>Job Description &amp; Requirements</p>\n<p>Operations</p>\n<p>- Assists in vessels's arrival and departure formalities.</p>\n<p>- Handle cargo documentation, invoices and shipments.</p>\n<p>- Familiarized with MPA’s latest governing rules &amp; regulations for anchorages, vessel movements, restrictions etc. within Singapore waters</p>\n<p>- Arrangement of harbor tugs, booking of PSA pilotage via system, arrangement of crew for port &amp; immigration clearance, declaration of vessel’s arrival via MPA’s Marinet and etc.</p>\n<p>- Oversee MPA applications on Marinet Portal</p>\n<p>Requirement</p>\n<p>- Candidate must possess at least “O” Level, Diploma or equivalent</p>\n<p>- At least 1 year of working experience, preferably in the Marine Agency</p>\n<p>- Meticulous and comfortable working in fast paced environment</p>\n<p>- Must be willing to take calls after office hours</p>\n<p>- Good command in written and spoken English</p>\n<p>- Ability to effectively communicate with all level of the organization</p>\n<p>- IT savvy and proficient in Microsoft Office with experience in any in-house ERP system</p>",
